{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_060.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hellooo! Whoa, this is a lot of books..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Let me tell you this in advance..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "What I hate most of all is to be interrupted while I'm working."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x92,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Especially when people talk to me while I'm reading. I find that to be most irritating."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...But even with that being said, it's you, and you probably wouldn't leave quietly anyway."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry... I don't get that many opportunities to talk to you, so I just can't help myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Still, this is a lot of books. Are you going to read all of these ones, too?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It's like you're going to read all the books in the entire library."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Naturally. I came here for that very reason."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Although, I've read the majority of the books here before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "There aren't that many books that I still need to look through."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I-I see... You're so amazing,<CR>Mr. Keith..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I don't think I could remember the contents of all these books..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Do you normally forget the contents of books you've read? That's rare..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I think it's more rare to be able to remember everything..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "There are little tricks to reading. Tricks to read fast, and tricks to remember the contents."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, but there's no need to lecture you on reading methods. Now, liberate me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "(I don't have that many opportunities to talk to Mr. Keith. I need to think of a topic...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "...Oh, the book you're reading, it's the one about our local folklore, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I've read that one before as well!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "...What?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I'm in the process of reading through all the literature unique to this land, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I see, so you've already read this one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "That book was really interesting. Especially in Chapter 3, where‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x95,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Stop! It irritates me to no end that there is some knowledge that you know, but I don't."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x97,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I'd like for you to refrain from talking to me until I finish reading this book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "(He scolded me. But, Mr. Keith was surprisingly...)"
        }
    ]
}